      "stem": "(x^2 - 4)/(x + 2)",
      "answer": "x - 2",
      "answerLatex": "x - 2",
      "solutionSteps": [
        "Factorise the numerator (difference of squares): x^2 - 4 = (x - 2)(x + 2).",
